Class CSS.V

java.lang.Object
  org.cobogw.gwt.user.client.CSS.V
Enclosing class:
CSS
public static final class CSS.V
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains all named (i.e. String) values grouped by the property. The values AUTO, NONE and INHERIT are supported on multiple properties and are not separately put in a class when only the property and other numeric property values are valid.
